text: William Bull (1886 - 1970) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1886 births Category:1970 deaths Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
